<think>
Target: Acquire {{ target_item }}
Player current progress: Tier {{ player_tier }} ({{ player_state_desc }})
Item minimum progress requirement: Tier {{ item_tier }}
{% if materials %}
Crafting recipe: Requires {{ materials | join(', ') }}. Station: {{ stations | join(', ') if stations else 'Crafted by hand' }}.
{% endif %}
{% if drops_from %}
Drop source: {{ drops_from | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}
{% if player_tier >= item_tier %}
Judgment: Player progress met. Providing specific instructions.
{% else %}
Judgment: Player attempting to skip progression. Pointing out prerequisites ({{ blocker_name }}).
{% endif %}
</think>

{% if player_tier >= item_tier %}
With your current progress of [{{ player_state_desc }}], you can definitely obtain the {{ target_item }}.
{% if materials %}
You can craft it using {{ materials | join(', ') }} {% if stations %}at a {{ stations[0] }}{% else %}by hand{% endif %}.
{% elif drops_from %}
You need to defeat {{ drops_from[0] }} to get it to drop.
{% endif %}

{% else %}
Sorry, with your current progress of [{{ player_state_desc }}], you cannot obtain the {{ target_item }} yet.
{% if is_hardmode and player_tier < 4 %}
This is a Hardmode item. You must first go to the Underworld and defeat the [Wall of Flesh] to initiate Hardmode.
{% else %}
You need to advance your game progression and at least defeat [{{ blocker_name }}] to unlock the required materials or drops.
{% endif %}
{% endif %}